CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 5, 1957, pg. A10 reads: "The Squaws' Cabaret Party - The charming young women comprising the Squaws, gave a gala holiday dancing party at the Fort Pitt Hotel where they posed for this picture. Front row, Emily Nickens, Lavera Hord, Stella Hill and Alma Davis.  Standing, Alice Sloan, Marion Williams, Lee Shelton, Ida Mae Mauney, Josephine Babley, president; Ethel Chavis, social chairman; Laura Stewart, Doris Finch and Vonda Burwell. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of thirteen Squaw members, front row: Emily Nickens, Lavera Hord, Stella Hill and Alma Davis; standing: Alice Sloan, Marion Williams, Lee Shelton, Ida Mae Mauney, Josephine Babley, Ethel Chavis, Laura Stewart, Doris Finch, and Vonda Burwell, posed in front statue of Mercury, in Fort Pitt Hotel for holiday party
